_sText:
Its winter time and counter-terrorist are enjoying their time inside warm cabin. Nearby train carrying biohazard materials gets stuck on the snow and terrorist are about to attack!

Counter-terrorist:
Defend the cabin and the train!

Terrorist:
Eliminate all counter-terrorists and try to plant bomb in the train or the cabin!

Plants:
A in the sauna
B end of the train

Enjoy the map and remember to leave feedback or report possible bugs!
